metadata.name: Hide In The Light
metadata.description:
“Even you are in the darkness cave in your mind, you can still have a light spot on.
Even you are in the spotlight, you still can hide by closing your eyes.
Even in that place is truly cold, you are still alive if you have a warm heart in your soul.
There is always hope awaiting.”
The part of Moonseeker Comics series describes about the character name Shun. She is the
one of Moonseeker team who is half human and robot. She has a heart, feeling and love but the
shell (body) makes her become a cyborg. She is in another universe but she still seeking for the
moon. The moon that not in our planet, which is call earth.

Artist: Nopper/Rozalin
Type: Collaborative artwork
